scopecontent.p:
The collection is composed of reminiscences of the Swan Land and
		  Cattle Company. The bundles of material are entitled: 
		The Swan Land and Cattle Company. Utilizers of Wyoming
		  Grass; 
		The Swan Company roundups Parts I and II; 
		The Two-Bar hands. Cowboys for the Swan Company; 
		Blue Grass Well. World's largest water-hole; and 
		Edward Held and the Swan Company.
